2
00:00:06,370 --> 00:00:09,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu adalah kursi paling kesepian di dunia.</font>

3
00:00:12,630 --> 00:00:14,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Semua abdimu...</font>

4
00:00:14,970 --> 00:00:17,210
<font color=#FFFF00>...akan memberikan pendapat berbeda.</font>

5
00:00:18,240 --> 00:00:20,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa yang harus kau dengarkan?</font>

6
00:00:20,410 --> 00:00:22,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Mana yang benar?</font>

7
00:00:22,340 --> 00:00:25,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Akan tiba saat kau tidak lagi mengetahuinya.</font>

8
00:00:28,910 --> 00:00:30,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila saat itu tiba,</font>

9
00:00:31,270 --> 00:00:33,210
<font color=#FFFF00>apa yang harus saya lakukan?</font>

10
00:00:36,670 --> 00:00:37,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Cukup...</font>

11
00:00:39,470 --> 00:00:41,370
<font color=#FFFF00>...dengarkan suara hatimu.</font>

12
00:00:45,870 --> 00:00:47,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak ada...</font>

13
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:50,140
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang akan mengambil keputusan untukmu.</font>

14
00:00:50,140 --> 00:00:53,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak ada pula yang akan bertanggungjawab atas dirimu.</font>

15
00:00:54,170 --> 00:00:57,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah... Raja.</font>

16
00:01:03,140 --> 00:01:05,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha.</font>

17
00:01:05,510 --> 00:01:10,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha! Anda tidak boleh melewatkan kesempatan ini.</font>

18
00:01:15,940 --> 00:01:17,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

19
00:01:20,940 --> 00:01:22,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Pyunsoo-hwe...</font>

20
00:01:23,310 --> 00:01:24,910
<font color=#FFFF00>...akan kuserang.</font>

21
00:01:34,610 --> 00:01:37,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan membalaskan dendam ayah dan ibuku.</font>

22
00:01:40,970 --> 00:01:43,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan membalaskan Ayah Guru Chung Woon.</font>

23
00:01:48,140 --> 00:01:51,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Juga dendam Gyu Ho Eureushin.</font>

24
00:01:52,940 --> 00:01:56,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang juga, aku ingin menyerang
Dae Mok dan Pyunsoo-hwe.</font>

25
00:02:04,070 --> 00:02:08,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Jae Hon sungguh mengatakan akan menggerakkan pasukannya?</font>

26
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:09,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, itu benar.</font>

27
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:12,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat itu akhirnya tiba.</font>

28
00:02:12,540 --> 00:02:15,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, kita bisa melenyapkan Pyunsoo-hwe
dalam sekali libas.</font>

29
00:02:15,770 --> 00:02:18,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya tidak menyangka saat ini akhirnya tiba.</font>

30
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:21,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Bahkan Dae Mok sekalipun...</font>

31
00:02:21,470 --> 00:02:25,170
<font color=#FFFF00>...tak akan sanggup menandingi pasukan Jenderal Jae Hon.</font>

32
00:02:26,810 --> 00:02:30,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Anda sekarang memiliki 40.000 pasukan
dalam genggaman, Daebi Mama.</font>

33
00:02:30,270 --> 00:02:33,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa lagi yang mampu menandingi Anda?</font>

34
00:02:33,610 --> 00:02:36,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya ucapkan selamat, Mama.</font>

35
00:02:43,670 --> 00:02:45,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha.</font>

36
00:02:50,140 --> 00:02:51,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun,</font>

37
00:02:53,340 --> 00:02:54,870
<font color=#FFFF00>aku pun...</font>

38
00:02:56,940 --> 00:02:58,470
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidak bisa.</font>

39
00:03:10,410 --> 00:03:13,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita tidak benar-benar tahu kekuatan Pyunsoo-hwe.</font>

40
00:03:13,810 --> 00:03:16,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Bahkan dengan bantuan pasukan perbatasan sekalipun,</font>

41
00:03:16,810 --> 00:03:18,910
<font color=#FFFF00>aku tidak yakin kita bisa memberantas...</font>

42
00:03:18,910 --> 00:03:20,710
<font color=#FFFF00>...mereka sampai ke akar.</font>

43
00:03:20,710 --> 00:03:23,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mungkin merebut mahkota dan takhta,</font>

44
00:03:23,340 --> 00:03:24,540
<font color=#FFFF00>namun...</font>

45
00:03:26,140 --> 00:03:29,110
<font color=#FFFF00>...ribuan rakyat mungkin akan cedera,</font>

46
00:03:31,070 --> 00:03:32,610
<font color=#FFFF00>atau bahkan tewas.</font>

47
00:03:34,370 --> 00:03:36,510
<font color=#FFFF00>- Jeoha!
- Juga...</font>

48
00:03:37,670 --> 00:03:39,710
<font color=#FFFF00>bila pemerintahan kacau,</font>

49
00:03:40,270 --> 00:03:41,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Suku Jurchen (nenek moyang Manchuria,
selalu berusaha menjajah Joseon],</font>

50
00:03:41,740 --> 00:03:44,470
<font color=#FFFF00>tak akan tinggal diam.</font>

51
00:03:45,270 --> 00:03:46,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Seorang Raja yang menimbulkan kerusuhan...</font>

52
00:03:46,670 --> 00:03:49,440
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan peperangan di dalam negerinya?</font>

53
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:50,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

54
00:03:52,210 --> 00:03:54,540
<font color=#FFFF00>...tak mau menjadi Raja seperti itu.</font>

55
00:04:01,740 --> 00:04:03,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasukanmu di perbatasan,</font>

56
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:06,710
<font color=#FFFF00>akan tetap di sana.</font>

57
00:04:06,710 --> 00:04:08,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha.</font>

58
00:04:08,340 --> 00:04:11,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Mohon pertimbangkan kembali.</font>

59
00:04:11,910 --> 00:04:14,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila mendiang Raja masih hidup,</font>

60
00:04:14,010 --> 00:04:17,070
<font color=#FFFF00>beliau pasti memerintah untuk menyerang Pyunsoo-hwe,</font>

61
00:04:17,070 --> 00:04:19,040
<font color=#FFFF00>tanpa ragu sama sekali.</font>

62
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:21,510
<font color=#FFFF00>"Jangan menunjukkan ketakutan di hadapan siapapun."</font>

63
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:23,240
<font color=#FFFF00>"Tutupi kelemahan dengan kekuatan..."</font>

64
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:25,240
<font color=#FFFF00>"...serta ketakutan dengan keberanian."</font>

65
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,770
<font color=#FFFF00>"Itulah Raja."</font>

66
00:04:28,010 --> 00:04:32,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah yang mendiang ayahku katakan.</font>

67
00:04:32,570 --> 00:04:35,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi... Joseon-ku...</font>

68
00:04:36,910 --> 00:04:38,410
<font color=#FFFF00>...akan berbeda.</font>

69
00:04:39,610 --> 00:04:42,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila harus mengorbankan rakyat,</font>

70
00:04:42,770 --> 00:04:45,010
<font color=#FFFF00>aku tak akan mengambil kembali takhta itu.</font>

71
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:51,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

72
00:04:53,180 --> 00:04:56,210
<font color=#FFFF00>...akan menjadi Raja yang memedulikan rakyatnya.</font>

73
00:04:56,510 --> 00:04:59,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Rakyat adalah prioritasku.</font>

74
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:03,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa aku mengambil alih takhta
dengan menumpahkan darah mereka?</font>

75
00:05:03,570 --> 00:05:05,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha.</font>

76
00:05:05,970 --> 00:05:07,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila kau...</font>

77
00:05:10,010 --> 00:05:12,770
<font color=#FFFF00>...mengganggapku sebagai Raja sejati,</font>

78
00:05:15,310 --> 00:05:17,770
<font color=#FFFF00>maka percayalah padaku dan kembali ke perbatasan.</font>

79
00:05:17,770 --> 00:05:19,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan melindungiku,</font>

80
00:05:21,470 --> 00:05:23,240
<font color=#FFFF00>tapi rakyatku.</font>

81
00:05:24,870 --> 00:05:26,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong lakukan itu.</font>

82
00:05:42,910 --> 00:05:44,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya...</font>

83
00:05:45,270 --> 00:05:48,140
<font color=#FFFF00>...Komandan Militer Jae Hon,</font>

84
00:05:48,610 --> 00:05:52,310
<font color=#FFFF00>akan mematuhi titah Paduka.</font>

85
00:06:33,070 --> 00:06:34,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu itu?</font>

86
00:06:35,340 --> 00:06:37,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tak akan memanggil pasukanmu?</font>

87
00:06:39,310 --> 00:06:40,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Jenderal.</font>

88
00:06:40,610 --> 00:06:42,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau takut pada Pyunsoo-hwe,</font>

89
00:06:42,640 --> 00:06:46,170
<font color=#FFFF00>atau memang loyalitasmu serendah itu?</font>

90
00:06:46,170 --> 00:06:49,070
<font color=#FFFF00>- Mama.
- Sudah kuberi izin memanggil pasukanmu,</font>

91
00:06:49,270 --> 00:06:51,740
<font color=#FFFF00>tapi sampai kini kau belum melakukannya?</font>

92
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:53,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Selain izin dariku,</font>

93
00:06:53,970 --> 00:06:55,970
<font color=#FFFF00>memang perintah siapa yang lebih penting?</font>

94
00:06:55,970 --> 00:06:57,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja Jeoha.</font>

95
00:07:03,510 --> 00:07:04,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Barusan...</font>

96
00:07:06,070 --> 00:07:08,210
<font color=#FFFF00>...apa yang kau katakan?</font>

97
00:07:08,940 --> 00:07:10,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja?</font>

98
00:07:13,970 --> 00:07:15,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan bilang...</font>

99
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:18,310
<font color=#FFFF00>...Seja sesungguhnya...</font>

100
00:07:18,410 --> 00:07:20,770
<font color=#FFFF00>...masih hidup?</font>

101
00:07:20,770 --> 00:07:22,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Seperti itulah, Mama.</font>

102
00:07:23,310 --> 00:07:27,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa kau tidak memberitahu aku lebih awal?</font>

103
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:29,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebelum saya mengonfirmasinya sendiri,</font>

104
00:07:29,640 --> 00:07:31,840
<font color=#FFFF00>saya tidak bisa mengatakan apa-apa.</font>

105
00:07:32,170 --> 00:07:33,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila...</font>

106
00:07:33,710 --> 00:07:37,310
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia bukanlah Seja yang asli,</font>

107
00:07:37,410 --> 00:07:39,010
<font color=#FFFF00>maka saya pasti sudah mematuhi Mama,</font>

108
00:07:39,310 --> 00:07:43,210
<font color=#FFFF00>dan memanggil pasukan saya untuk membalas dendam
mendiang Raja serta Seja Jeoha.</font>

109
00:07:46,140 --> 00:07:47,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Sungguh...</font>

110
00:07:49,270 --> 00:07:52,170
<font color=#FFFF00>...Seja masih hidup?</font>

111
00:07:56,570 --> 00:07:58,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Pangeranku...</font>

112
00:07:58,510 --> 00:08:01,570
<font color=#FFFF00>...selama ini masih hidup?</font>

113
00:08:03,310 --> 00:08:06,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja-ku sehat dan baik-baik saja?</font>

114
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:10,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah dia sedang sakit...</font>

115
00:08:10,970 --> 00:08:13,140
<font color=#FFFF00>...atau terluka parah?</font>

116
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:15,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan cemas, Mama.</font>

117
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:18,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Mama pun sudah bertemu dengan Seja asli,</font>

118
00:08:18,740 --> 00:08:20,510
<font color=#FFFF00>secara langsung.</font>

119
00:08:22,410 --> 00:08:25,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Kepala Pedagang keliling yang membantu Mama,</font>

120
00:08:25,610 --> 00:08:28,010
<font color=#FFFF00>adalah Seja Jeoha yang asli.</font>

121
00:08:35,210 --> 00:08:37,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa dia begitu mirip dengan...</font>

122
00:08:38,470 --> 00:08:41,070
<font color=#FFFF00>...mendiang Raja saat muda?</font>

123
00:08:59,970 --> 00:09:02,140
<font color=#FFFF00>- Orabeoni.
- Daebi Mama.</font>

124
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:04,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang yang adikmu ini katakan,</font>

125
00:09:06,140 --> 00:09:07,810
<font color=#FFFF00>tolong dengar baik-baik.</font>

126
00:09:10,540 --> 00:09:14,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika ini tersebar, Orabeoni, aku,</font>

127
00:09:15,940 --> 00:09:20,710
<font color=#FFFF00>maupun seluruh keluarga kita akan hancur.</font>

128
00:09:24,780 --> 00:09:26,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mengerti?</font>

129
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau pergi ke Heopgyeongdang,</font>

130
00:09:33,780 --> 00:09:36,610
<font color=#FFFF00>ada tamu Daebi Mama yang sedang menunggu.</font>

131
00:09:36,710 --> 00:09:39,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Bawakan makanan ringan ini untuknya.</font>

132
00:09:39,970 --> 00:09:41,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Mama-nim.</font>

133
00:10:01,810 --> 00:10:02,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun-ah.</font>

134
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:19,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak akan tanya apa-apa.</font>

135
00:10:27,710 --> 00:10:30,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai aku selesai meminum tehku,</font>

136
00:10:33,280 --> 00:10:37,210
<font color=#FFFF00>bisakah kau tetap berada di sini?</font>

137
00:11:10,210 --> 00:11:11,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Sepertinya,</font>

138
00:11:12,140 --> 00:11:15,940
<font color=#FFFF00>kau masih senang menggoda dayang istana.</font>

139
00:11:17,870 --> 00:11:19,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Lain waktu, aku akan melaporkannya.</font>

140
00:11:23,040 --> 00:11:24,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tak bisa menghabiskannya...</font>

141
00:11:29,140 --> 00:11:30,570
<font color=#FFFF00>...sampai tetes terakhir.</font>

142
00:12:51,970 --> 00:12:53,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Doryongnim.</font>

143
00:15:09,770 --> 00:15:14,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Daebi Mama, Busang Daegam datang menemui Anda.</font>

144
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:15,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Biarkan dia masuk.</font>

145
00:15:18,270 --> 00:15:19,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana?</font>

146
00:15:19,940 --> 00:15:23,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, kami mengurusnya sesuai instruksi Mama.</font>

147
00:15:26,370 --> 00:15:28,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Kerja bagus.</font>

148
00:15:59,670 --> 00:16:02,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun-ah! Cepat bangun.</font>

149
00:16:02,440 --> 00:16:03,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun-ah!</font>

150
00:16:05,670 --> 00:16:06,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun-ah.</font>

151
00:16:25,310 --> 00:16:26,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Doryongnim.</font>

152
00:16:27,040 --> 00:16:30,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun-ah. Kau baik-baik saja?</font>

153
00:16:32,810 --> 00:16:36,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku senang kau baik-baik saja.</font>

154
00:16:39,410 --> 00:16:40,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun, kau...</font>

155
00:16:43,310 --> 00:16:45,670
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang menyelamatkan aku?</font>

156
00:16:49,510 --> 00:16:52,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau hampir mati karena menyelamatkan aku.</font>

157
00:16:52,770 --> 00:16:54,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau melompat ke dalam air?</font>

158
00:16:55,140 --> 00:16:57,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau melakukan hal yang berbahaya?</font>

159
00:16:57,470 --> 00:16:58,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku takut.</font>

160
00:17:02,910 --> 00:17:05,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak bisa bertemu Doryongnim lagi,</font>

161
00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:07,810
<font color=#FFFF00>begitu menakutkan untukku.</font>

162
00:17:11,070 --> 00:17:13,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku takut akan kehilangan seseorang yang lebih berharga...</font>

163
00:17:16,140 --> 00:17:17,410
<font color=#FFFF00>..dibanding nyawaku.</font>

164
00:18:56,310 --> 00:18:59,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak bisa menemukan Ga Eun Aghassi?
Apa maksudmu?</font>

165
00:18:59,110 --> 00:19:01,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya yakin Ga Eun Aghassi pergi ke luar istana.</font>

166
00:19:02,340 --> 00:19:03,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang sudah pukul 10 malam.</font>

167
00:19:03,810 --> 00:19:06,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Semestinya dia sudah kembali sekarang.</font>

168
00:19:08,070 --> 00:19:10,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Semua gerbang akan ditutup pukul 10 malam.</font>

169
00:19:15,140 --> 00:19:16,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak apa-apa.</font>

170
00:19:17,310 --> 00:19:18,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Turunkan aku.</font>

171
00:19:18,870 --> 00:19:22,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah menyelamatkan nyawaku.
Setidaknya ini yang bisa kulakukan.</font>

172
00:19:29,070 --> 00:19:30,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku..</font>

173
00:19:31,140 --> 00:19:34,840
<font color=#FFFF00>...telah bersikap dingin dan menyakiti hatimu selama ini,</font>

174
00:19:35,910 --> 00:19:37,040
<font color=#FFFF00>maafkan aku.</font>

175
00:19:39,040 --> 00:19:40,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Sejujurnya...</font>

176
00:19:40,070 --> 00:19:42,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Tak apa. Aku memahaminya.</font>

177
00:19:44,170 --> 00:19:46,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita bicarakan itu nanti saja.</font>

178
00:19:47,710 --> 00:19:49,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak kedinginan.</font>

179
00:19:50,940 --> 00:19:53,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, aku merasa hangat.</font>

180
00:19:55,140 --> 00:19:56,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Bila memungkinkan,</font>

181
00:19:57,940 --> 00:20:01,510
<font color=#FFFF00>aku ingin waktu terhenti sekarang juga.</font>

182
00:20:02,480 --> 00:20:05,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku juga... menginginkan hal yang sama.</font>

183
00:20:12,070 --> 00:20:14,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan masuk.</font>

184
00:20:14,610 --> 00:20:15,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Haruskah...</font>

185
00:20:16,540 --> 00:20:18,940
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau kembali?</font>

186
00:20:25,770 --> 00:20:26,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Ga Eun-ah.</font>

187
00:20:27,840 --> 00:20:30,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa pun rencanamu di dalam sana,</font>

188
00:20:30,510 --> 00:20:34,610
<font color=#FFFF00>jangan melakukan hal yang berbahaya.</font>

189
00:20:36,070 --> 00:20:37,980
