275
00:27:48,210 --> 00:27:49,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mengerti maksudku, bukan?</font>

276
00:27:49,670 --> 00:27:51,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Cheonha.</font>

277
00:28:07,470 --> 00:28:08,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Cheonha.</font>

278
00:28:09,410 --> 00:28:13,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa sebenarnya Kepala Pedagang itu?
